5:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-blue-50 py-14","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-anton text-3xl uppercase mb-6 text-text-main text-center","children":["Local Roads and Driving Conditions in ","Seven Hills"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-10 text-center mx-auto","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"Looking for driving lessons in Seven Hills? UNO Driving School provides calm, automatic driving lessons for learners across Seven Hills, Norman Park, Morningside and Camp Hill. Our 5-star instructors help Seven Hills students pass their Queensland driving test on the first attempt."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"Seven Hills is a spectacularly quiet, deeply undulating enclave hidden centrally within the inner-east. True to its name, the suburb is intensely hilly. Surrounded entirely by busy surrounding suburbs, Seven Hills acts as an insulated island of calm, making it one of the premier locations in Brisbane for teaching basic and intermediate car control."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"Our instructors use the large gradients and completely empty residential grids here to train flawless hill starts, reverse parallel parking, and deep observation skills around blind crests. Once this confidence is secured, slipping out into the intensity of Morningside or Norman Park feels manageable, preparing a student perfectly for their Greenslopes TMR test."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Seven Hills learners sit their test at the Greenslopes TMR Customer Service Centre. Free pickup from Seven Hills, modern automatic vehicles, Afterpay available. Book today."}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border border-blue-100 flex items-start gap-4","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-primary text-xl mt-0.5","children":"📍"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["